		   <br /><nobr><span class="notbold">Score</span>: Good [3.92]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Aggrok&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>     I have a 54 Ogre shaman and enjoy soloing with him. I also have a level 8 DE necro which I dont play too much. My concerns about spending ALOT of time getting a necro to high level are as follows--<br />   1. It seems to me that there arent alot of high level necros on my server, telling me that people either get tired of them quick, or retire them early to start something else due to boredom.<br /><br />   2. I rarely see necros in full groups even tho they have alot of offensive spell capability and good pets. I NEVER see anyone in a forming group say &quot; Party of 4 seeks necromancer PST &quot;. Most time when I have seen a necro in a full group its because they are on the way to summon corpses from a nasty wiped in places like Chardok for example.<br /><br />   3. For that matter I rarely see necros solo much in high level zones either. Its my belief that for necros to solo well they basically have to fear kite mobs. I know of few places this can be done without the running mob eventually going by something else which would aggro into the fight. Shamans can ghetto fear with our blindness spell which will cause a mob to run ( if out of melee range ) as if it had been feared. I personally never use this spell even tho its low mana due to the short duration, resists, and getting adds with the returning mob. <br /><br />   If anyone whos played a necro to high level could reply to this post its much appreciated. Also would like to know what you all think is the best necro race. Thx in advance<br /><br />54 Ogre BattleMystic on Luclin server--Aggrok</p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br />64 Ogre Oracle on Luclin Server--Venerable Aggrok</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td><td align="right" id="fs8" >3 Replies</td></tr></table>
